                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Poster</Header>
                <Paragraph>An employer is required to post a notice describing the Federal laws that prohibit job discrimination based on age, color, disability, equal pay, genetic information, national origin, race, religion, or sex. The "Equal Employment Opportunity is THE LAW" poster contains a summary of these laws and explains how an employee or applicant can file a discrimination complaint. The EEOC's poster is available in Arabic, Chinese, English, and Spanish.</Paragraph>
